    	)

		USING UNNEST(d_id_in_array) AS d_ids

		  AND no_w_id = d_w_id

		       c_data = substr ((p_c_id || $16 ||
                                 p_c_d_id || $17 ||
                                 p_c_w_id || $18 ||
                                 p_d_id || $19 ||
